[30;1m485 | [0m[35m    running, rather then looking at the event loop which is installed when[0m
[30;1m486 | [0m[35m    `StdoutProxy` is created. This way, `patch_stdout` will work when[0m
[30;1m487 | [0m[35m    prompt_toolkit applications with a different event loop run.[0m

[30;1m104 | [0m[35mAbout Windows support[0m
[30;1m105 | [0m[35m*********************[0m
[30;1m106 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m107 | [0m[35m``prompt_toolkit`` is cross platform, and everything that you build on top[0m
[30;1m108 | [0m[35mshould run fine on both Unix and Windows systems. Windows support is best on[0m
